title: C(sp3)–H cyclizations of 2-(2-vinyl)phenoxy-tert-anilines
content:
RSC Adv., 2024, 14,16784-16800
DOI: 10.1039/D3RA08974F, Paper

Petra Dunkel, Dóra Bogdán, Ruth Deme, Ádám Zimber, Veronika Ballayová, Eszter Csizmadia, Bence Kontra, Eszter Kalydi, Attila Bényei, Péter Mátyus, Zoltán Mucsi
Cyclizations of 2-(2-vinyl)phenoxy-tert-anilines under thermal conditions yield oxazonine or octahydro-dipyrroloquinoline products. The transformations can be considered as further extensions of [1,n]-H transfer and cyclization of tertiary anilines.
